function rainbowize (offset) {
    // "use strict"; //no octal lit
    offset = offset || 0;
    return function () {
        const els = this,
            l = els.length,
            tpl = '\x1b[1;%code%m%char%\x1b[0m',
            cols = [
                31 + offset, // red
                32 + offset, // green
                33 + offset, // yellow
                34 + offset, // blue
                35 + offset, // magenta
                36 + offset, // cyan
                91 + offset, // lightred
                92 + offset, // lightgreen
                93 + offset, // lightyellow
                94 + offset, // lightblue
                95 + offset, // lightmagenta
                96 + offset // lightcyan
            ],
            out = [];
        let i = 0, j = 0;
        for (null; i < l; i++) {
            out.push(
                els[i] !== ' '
                    ? tpl.replace('%code%', cols[j++ % cols.length]).replace('%char%', els[i])
                    : els[i]
            );
        }
        return out.join('');
    };
}
 
function conc (n, inst) {
    return [
        '\x1b[1;',
        n,
        'm',
        inst,
        '\x1b[0m'
    ].join('');
}
